# Generated state (flake + caches); keep only the lock.
.state/*
!.state/flake.lock

# Local-only, hidden extras: dot-prefixed configs/modules are still loaded by
# IceDOS but never committed. Hidden config files (configs/.<name>.toml — the
# successor to .private.toml) and hidden loose modules (modules/.<name>.nix):
.*.nix
.*.toml
# Hidden folder-modules (modules/.<name>/ holding default.nix / icedos.nix):
modules/.*/
